  <brief_title>A Safety, Tolerability, and Efficacy Study of VX-880 in Participants With Type 1 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1/2 Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, and Efficacy of VX-880 in Subjects Who Have Type 1 Diabetes Mellitus With Impaired Hypoglycemic Awareness and Severe Hypoglycemia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
