  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the safety, tolerability and efficacy of VX-880 infusion in&#xD;
      participants with Type 1 diabetes mellitus (T1D) and impaired awareness of hypoglycemia (IAH)&#xD;
      and severe hypoglycemia.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
